She just looked so beautiful.

04:15.487 --> 04:17.853
I... I couldn't stop
the happiness.

04:17.856 --> 04:19.454
Yeah. You won't even consider

04:19.457 --> 04:21.589
trying that Zyrem,
Xyrem stuff again?

04:21.591 --> 04:24.060
It doesn't do any more for me
than exercise, Cooper

04:24.062 --> 04:26.563
and exercise doesn't
make me wet the bed.

04:26.565 --> 04:27.697
Alright.

04:27.699 --> 04:30.299
I just, you know..

04:30.301 --> 04:32.237
I don't want you to die.

04:33.639 --> 04:35.438
I'll be fine.

04:35.440 --> 04:37.877
As long as there are
no more weddings ever.

04:39.010 --> 04:40.844
I can count on you for that,
right?

04:40.846 --> 04:42.411
Hey.

04:42.413 --> 04:45.448
Oh, I saw, uh, Marvin's sister,
Rita, checking you out.

04:45.450 --> 04:47.017
- Was she now?
